
Internal design
================
This project contains several classes and one JUnit test class:

SaleTerminal.java is the point of sale scanning API, which scans products, sets product
price and calculate the final total price.
Productscanner.java is used to record all the product a customer purchased and including the quantity.
ProductCalculator.java is used to calculate the total price of a product with certain quantity.
DuplicatProduct.java is a runtimeException when the product already has a price policy.
MissingProduct.java is the product did not have a price policy.
TestCase.java is a JUnit test class used to test all the three test cases.

How to run
================
import the whole project "ScanningAPI" to Eclipse and find the TestCase class, press run button.
